description:
Kiyoura Setsuna is a student in year one of class three, who as http://anidb.net/ch2345 [Kotonoha], is on the student council as a class representative.
One of the more inscrutable characters, Setsuna is a keen, focused and habitually tacit girl who tends to have and keep the most level head of her peers when situations go awry.
name: Kiyoura Setsuna
